{"tid":2459182,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"挽救銷售 日本可口可樂推出自動販賣機月費訂閱服務 可每日自選飲料","createTime":"2021-03-24T04:01:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T04:12:54.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d17c469b916609419d2146d72b4e85d4d342041e","tid":2459182,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T04:01:34.000Z","msg":"財經頻道／綜合報導〕日本武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19）疫情大流行，導致可口可樂公司（Coca Cola）在日本的自動販賣機銷售節節下滑，為挽回業績，可口可樂公司推出自動售貨機包月訂閱新服務，消費者每月支付2700日圓（約新台幣718元），即可每天從自動售貨機領取1份自己喜歡的飲料。<br />\n<br />\n《日經新聞》報導，可口可樂新服務名稱「Coke ON Pass」，消費者只要在可口可樂手機APP找到「Coke ON」註冊並訂閱，即可每天從遍布在日本各地34萬部自動販賣機選取1份飲料。可口可樂在日本提供的茶點選擇眾多，像是黑咖啡、無糖茶和其他形式的茶飲，因此消費者不會僅侷限於可樂。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3476950\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3476950&d=bXICEjaVmsGxuRkiXhyD2OdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=b6af70b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3476950&h=65b6d5f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3476950</a>"},{"pid":"17bf44a11eb1f3981b35616d7aa3400b614021bb","tid":2459182,"uid":78243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T04:09:22.000Z","msg":"平均90円"},{"pid":"9cb49530b00dae612a1b109bac1ccbab4c9c35e5","tid":2459182,"uid":54502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T04:11:16.000Z","msg":"抵呀，冬天仲有熱飲"},{"pid":"b1958b4b0939cea8b7d316ba9bfd0c03923d27ce","tid":2459182,"uid":184787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T04:12:54.000Z","msg":"幾好，反正番工都會買野飲"}]}